data.title: [Solved] Who was awarded nobel prize for the discovery of electron?
data.meta_description:
The correct answer is J. J. Thompson.

Key Points:Joseph John Thomson is widely recognized as the discoverer of the electron.


	Thomson was
data.text:
-> OSSC CGL Prelims Exam Dates has been released for recruitment to the post of Combined Graduate Level Recruitment Examination for Group-B & Group-C Specialist Posts/Services-2023.

-> It will be held on 04.08.2024 (Sunday) in One Sitting through OMR mode.

-> The Computer Skill Test and Mathematics Skill Test will be conducted on 12th and 31st August 2024.

-> The OSSC CGL Exam 2024 is being conducted for 543 vacancies of various Group B and Group C posts under the Government of Odisha.

-> OSSC CGL Notification 2024 was released for 543 vacancies of Auditor, Junior Inspector, and other posts.

-> The selection process includes a Prelims, Mains, Skill Test, and Document Verification.

-> To score well in the exam, you may enhance your preparation by solving the OSSC CGL Previous Years' Papers.
